Package pkgMain

Class Garden

java.lang.Object
pkgMain.Garden
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Garden
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
The Garden class represents a garden with different conditions and can have plants placed and moved around in it.
Author:
rbila
